snippet.title: Binary Non Binary
snippet.description:
Top down puzzle where you control both characters with the same input. 
Explores the duality of genders.

My submission of the Global Game Jam 2022 Oslo
https://globalgamejam.org/2022/games/binary-non-binary-0

Repository:
https://github.com/Slideshow776/GGJ2022OSLO

Play it here on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=no.sandramoen.ggj2022oslo

Play it here on desktop and Android:
https://github.com/Slideshow776/GGJ2022OSLO/tree/master/release
